<h1 id="project-forms">Project forms</h1>

<h2 id="show-a-project-39-s-form">Show a project&rsquo;s form</h2>

<p>Returns the form for the given <code class="prettyprint">project_id</code>.</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://screendoor.dobt.co/api/projects/2/form?v=0&amp;api_key=d9763djh1274"</span>

<span class="c"># Example Response</span>
<span class="o">[</span>
  <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="s2">"id"</span>: <span class="s2">"ak01k23k"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"type"</span>: <span class="s2">"field"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"field_type"</span>: <span class="s2">"paragraph"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"label"</span>: <span class="s2">"Your Approach"</span>
  <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">]</span>

</code></pre>

<h3 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h3>

<p><code class="prettyprint">GET /projects/:project_id/form</code></p>

<h2 id="update-a-project-39-s-form">Update a project&rsquo;s form</h2>

<p>Updates the project&rsquo;s form.</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://screendoor.dobt.co/api/projects/2/form?v=0&amp;api_key=d9763djh1274"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  -X PUT <span class="se">\</span>
  -d <span class="nv">field_data</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">'[
{
  "id": "ak01k23k",
  "type": "field",
  "field_type": "text",
  "label": "Your Strategy"
}
]'</span>

<span class="c"># Example Response</span>
<span class="o">[</span>
  <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="s2">"id"</span>: <span class="s2">"ak01k23k"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"type"</span>: <span class="s2">"field"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"field_type"</span>: <span class="s2">"paragraph"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"label"</span>: <span class="s2">"Your Approach"</span>
  <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">]</span>

</code></pre>

<h3 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h3>

<p><code class="prettyprint">PUT /projects/:project_id/form</code></p>

<h3 id="options">Options</h3>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Default</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>field_data</td>
<td>JSON-encoded Array</td>
<td></td>
<td>Sorry, the form schema is not yet documented.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<h2 id="add-a-field-to-the-form">Add a field to the form</h2>

<p>Adds a single field to the project&rsquo;s form. You can manually specify an <code class="prettyprint">id</code> in the <code class="prettyprint">field_data</code> hash, or you can leave it blank to have one created for you.</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://screendoor.dobt.co/api/projects/2/form/fields?v=0&amp;api_key=d9763djh1274"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  -X POST <span class="se">\</span>
  -d <span class="nv">position</span><span class="o">=</span>0 <span class="se">\</span>
  -d <span class="nv">field_data</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">'
{
  "type": "field",
  "field_type": "text",
  "label": "Your Strategy"
}'</span>

<span class="c"># Example Response</span>
<span class="o">[</span>
  <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="s2">"id"</span>: <span class="s2">"ak01k23k"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"type"</span>: <span class="s2">"field"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"field_type"</span>: <span class="s2">"paragraph"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"label"</span>: <span class="s2">"Your Approach"</span>
  <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">]</span>

</code></pre>

<h3 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h3>

<p><code class="prettyprint">POST /projects/:project_id/form/fields</code></p>

<h3 id="options">Options</h3>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Default</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>field_data</td>
<td>JSON-encoded Hash</td>
<td></td>
<td>Sorry, the form schema is not yet documented.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>position</td>
<td>Integer</td>
<td></td>
<td>The zero-indexed position where this field should be inserted in the form. By default, it will be inserted as the last field in the form.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<h2 id="update-a-field-in-the-form">Update a field in the form</h2>

<p>Updates a single field in the project&rsquo;s form.</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://screendoor.dobt.co/api/projects/2/form/fields/ak01k23k?v=0&amp;api_key=d9763djh1274"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  -X PUT <span class="se">\</span>
  -d <span class="nv">field_data</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">'
{
  "type": "field",
  "field_type": "text",
  "label": "Your Strategy"
}'</span>

<span class="c"># Example Response</span>
<span class="o">[</span>
  <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="s2">"id"</span>: <span class="s2">"ak01k23k"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"type"</span>: <span class="s2">"field"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"field_type"</span>: <span class="s2">"paragraph"</span>,
    <span class="s2">"label"</span>: <span class="s2">"Your Approach"</span>
  <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">]</span>

</code></pre>

<h3 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h3>

<p><code class="prettyprint">PUT /projects/:project_id/form/fields/:id</code></p>

<h3 id="options">Options</h3>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Default</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>field_data</td>
<td>JSON-encoded Hash</td>
<td></td>
<td>Sorry, the form schema is not yet documented.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<h2 id="delete-a-field-from-the-form">Delete a field from the form</h2>

<p>Deletes a single field from the project&rsquo;s form.</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://screendoor.dobt.co/api/projects/2/form/fields/ak01k23k?v=0&amp;api_key=d9763djh1274"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  -X DELETE

<span class="c"># Example Response</span>
Status: 204 No Content
</code></pre>

<h3 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h3>

<p><code class="prettyprint">DELETE /projects/:project_id/form/fields/:id</code></p>
